import React from "react" import EosLogo from "../Assets/eos-logo.png" import AbernathyLogo from "../Assets/abernathy-logo.png" import PurpleGradient from "../Assets/purple-gradient.png" import OrangeGradient from "../Assets/orange-gradient.png" import "../Styles/StampPreview.css" function StampPreview(props) { const { jobName, jobCode, preparedFor, preparedBy, date, isRevision, jobPhase, gradientStyle, revisionNumber, disclaimer, showPageNumbers, } = props const formatRevisionNumber = (number) => { return String(number).padStart(2, "0") } const displayLogo = preparedBy === "Eos Lightmedia" ? EosLogo : preparedBy === "Abernathy Lighting Design" ? AbernathyLogo : null const getGradientStyle = (gradient) => { switch (gradient) { case "Purple/Blue": return { backgroundImage: `url(${PurpleGradient})`, backgroundPosition: "bottom left", backgroundRepeat: "no-repeat", backgroundSize: "cover", } case "Yellow/Green": return { backgroundImage: `url(${OrangeGradient})`, backgroundPosition: "bottom left", backgroundRepeat: "no-repeat", backgroundSize: "cover", } default: return {} } } console.log(disclaimer) const previewStyle = getGradientStyle(gradientStyle) const getDisclaimerText = (disclaimerValue) => { console.log(typeof disclaimerValue) switch (disclaimerValue) { case "1": return "Disclaimer: This document is for bid purposes only." case "2": console.log("case 2") return "This document is for review and not for construction." case "3": return "This is a generic disclaimer." default: return "" // No disclaimer for 0 or any other unspecified value } } const disclaimerText = getDisclaimerText(disclaimer) return (

Project Phase {jobPhase}

{displayLogo && ( )}

{disclaimerText}{" "}

{isRevision ? "Revision Date" : "Issued Date"}:{" "} {date} {isRevision && ( <> {" | "} Rev:{" "} {formatRevisionNumber(revisionNumber)} )}

{showPageNumbers && (

)}
) } export default StampPreview
